<?xml version="1.0"?><?mso-application progid="Excel.Sheet"?><Workbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns:ss="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><DocumentProperties xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><LastAuthor>Djurre van Dijk</LastAuthor><Created>2019-05-06T09:39:18Z</Created><LastSaved>2019-05-06T09:39:18Z</LastSaved><Version>16.00</Version></DocumentProperties><OfficeDocumentSettings xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><AllowPNG/></OfficeDocumentSettings><ExcelWorkbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><WindowHeight>9150</WindowHeight><WindowWidth>21570</WindowWidth><WindowTopX>32767</WindowTopX><WindowTopY>32767</WindowTopY><ProtectStructure>False</ProtectStructure><ProtectWindows>False</ProtectWindows></ExcelWorkbook><Styles><Style ss:ID="Default" ss:Name="Normal"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Bottom"/><Borders/><Font ss:FontName="Calibri" x:CharSet="238" x:Family="Swiss" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#000000"/><Interior/><NumberFormat/><Protection/></Style></Styles><Worksheet ss:Name="Script"><Table x:FullColumns="1" x:FullRows="1" ss:DefaultRowHeight="15"><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DOMINATION_VICTORY</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES column contains info on what text between { } signs means (if applicable). It usually stands for either a numeric value, or a numeric value with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VICTORY_CONDITION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Domination</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dominacja</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The name of the victory condition (which is to dominate the planet by capturing all sectors)</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VICTORY_CONDITION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Players can win this game by controlling a set number of the planet's  sectors, which they must subsequently hold until a countdown completes. </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gracz może zwyciężyć w tej rozgrywce, przejmując kontrolę nad wyznaczoną liczbą sektorów planety i utrzymując ją do końca odliczania. </Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The description of the victory condition.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OBJECTIVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OCCUPY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Occupy sectors: {INT_Count} / {INT_Total} </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zajmij sektory – {INT_Count}/{INT_Total} </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OBJECTIVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HOLD</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Hold sectors: {INT_Count} / {INT_Total} [turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Utrzymaj sektory – {INT_Count}/{INT_Total} – [turn/]</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_SECTOR_PERCENTAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">YOU</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">You control {INT_Percentage} % of sectors required for victory.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kontrolujesz {INT_Percentage}% sektorów wymaganych do zwycięstwa.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears in an event when you control certain percentage of sectors</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_SECTOR_PERCENTAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLAYER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} controls {INT_Percentage} % of sectors required for victory.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} kontroluje {INT_Percentage}% sektorów wymaganych do zwycięstwa.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">RETRANSLATION NOTE: Previoulsy this said "All Sectors", now it refers only to the sectors that the player needs to get in order to fulfil the victory condition.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_ENTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">YOU</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">You entered the final stage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wchodzisz w końcową fazę</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears in an event when you enter the final stage of the domination victory</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_ENTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLAYER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} entered the final stage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gracz {STR_Player} wchodzi w końcową fazę</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears in an event when a player enters the final stage of the domination victory</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_LEAVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">YOU</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">You left the final stage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Opuszczasz końcową fazę</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears in an event when you leave the final stage of the domination victory</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_LEAVE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLAYER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} left the final stage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gracz {STR_Player} opuszcza końcową fazę</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears in an event when a player leaves the final stage of the domination victory</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_TICK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">YOU</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Victory in {INT_Turns}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zwycięstwo za {INT_Turns}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears when you get closer to the domination victory while in final stage</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_TICK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PLAYER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} is victorious in {INT_Turns}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} zwycięży za {INT_Turns}[turn/]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The text that appears when a player gets closer to the domination victory while in final stage</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_TICK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEFEAT_OPPONENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">To cancel the impending victory of {STR_Player} you need to capture {INT_Count} of their {INT_Total} sectors.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Aby uniemożliwić zwycięstwo graczowi {STR_Player}, musisz zdobyć {INT_Count} z należących do niego {INT_Total} sektorów.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EVENT_FINAL_STAGE_TICK</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALLY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">To protect your allied victory you need to help {STR_Player} defend your sectors.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{STR_Player} potrzebuje twojej pomocy, by obronić sektory i zwycięstwo przymierza.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, text refers to a person that can either be male or female. If relevant for translation, please use the ‘localized string’ column for the male text and the ‘alternative localized string’ column for the female text.</Data></Cell></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><Unsynced/><Selected/><ProtectObjects>False</ProtectObjects><ProtectScenarios>False</ProtectScenarios></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>